A GSU officer based at Boni Forest in Lamu was shot dead by a colleague after a disagreement on Monday night.The sergeant who was of the Basuba base was killed by a constable.Earlier reports indicated he was killed in a case of mistaken identity after failing to respond to a security challenge. Police are yet to issue a statement on the incident.The constable was disarmed and arrested pending investigations.The body was airlifted to Nairobi.More to follow